flowchart TD
    IN["User input"] --> GA["Input guardrails<br/>before_agent / PII / prompt injection"]
    GA --> AG["Agent execution"]
    AG --> GT["Tool guardrails<br/>HITL / allowlist / runtime checks"]
    GT --> GO["Output guardrails<br/>after_agent / redact / quality checks"]
    GO --> OUT["Final response"]

    GA -. block .-> FAIL1["Reject / sanitize input"]
    GT -. stop .-> FAIL2["Ask approval / deny tool call"]
    GO -. rewrite .-> FAIL3["Mask / regenerate output"]

